american pork congress to be overhaul in 1988 the nation pork produc council , nppc , announc at thi year 's american pork congress , apc , that the congress and trade show will be divid into two part in 1988. next year apc , held in atlanta , will be a busi session onli and will continu to be the first week of march . the trade show is be chang into a new intern event call the world pork expo . the first expo will be held in june 1988 in de moin with an expand format , they said . execut vice-presid orvil sweet said the decis to spilt the show and congress came about becaus there are produc who never get to see the trade show floor . `` it make sens that we divid the busi session from the trade show , '' sweet said .